  "response": "The idea that Donald Trump is secretly a Democrat is a conspiracy theory and not supported by concrete evidence. Trump has been a prominent figure in the Republican Party and ran as its candidate in the 2016 and 2020 presidential elections. While he has made statements or taken positions at times that could be interpreted as moderate or aligned with certain Democratic views, these instances have generally been within the context of broader political strategy or personal beliefs.\n\nPolitical affiliations and opinions can be complex, and individuals may hold a range of views that do not strictly align with one party's platform. It's important to analyze statements and actions in their context rather than ascribing secret affiliations without clear evidence.",
